headline: Is It Too Late To Consider CBRE After Its Strong Multi Year Share Price Rally?
summary: Wondering if CBRE Group is still a smart way to ride the commercial real estate cycle, or if most of the upside is already priced in? You are not alone. The stock has cooled slightly in the last week with a -2.1% move, but it is still up 2.2% over 30 days and 20.1% year to date, building on 14.8% over 1 year, 95.4% over 3 years, and 135.9% over 5 years.
